QuestData.Title: Revered Among the Cenarion Expedition
QuestData.Description: We've taken notice of your accomplishments, $n. What you've done for us goes beyond what we expect from our allies.$B$BI've a special request to ask of you, but I must test your dedication first.
QuestData.LogDescription: Ysiel Windsinger at the Cenarion Refuge wants you to become revered with the Cenarion Expedition.
